Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
metric_capture..._average_paths(25.10)  metric_capture..._average_paths(25.10)

Name
       metric_capture_wns_average_paths

Syntax
        metric_capture_wns_average_paths <paths>

       Default: ""

       Specifies  a  list  of integers defining the number of paths to use for
       average wns metric capture.

       Example

       The following command:

       set_db metric_capture_wns_average_paths "100 300 500"

       Captures the following metrics (in part):

       timing.setup.wns.avgpath:100.path_group:reg2reg

       timing.setup.wns.avgpath:300.path_group:reg2reg

       timing.setup.wns.avgpath:300.path_group:reg2reg

